About Commercial Circle

Buy. Sell. Business

Started by a passionate business owner, Commercial Circle was born in 2006 to offer business owners a fast but powerful way of selling their business. Commercial Circle has come to offer simple yet powerful tools - bundled in the most cost effective package. On top of that, our trusted teams eagerly work with sellers to overcome the biggest problems in selling a business, all in-order to get connected to the ideal buyer they’re looking for.
